<h1>Pokémon abilities</h1>

<div class="intro">
	<p>Each ability from the latest generation of Pokémon games is listed below, along with a short
	description and how many Pokémon can have that ability. Click an ability name to see the Pokémon
	that can learn it.
	<p class="small">For new abilities from the upcoming games, see the <a href="/x-y">Pokemon X&amp;Y</a> page.

